title: deserving to win
body: can you guys look at my match history and tell me if my scores are any good because i keep winning game and climbing but i feel as tho i am bad and just get lucky every game or i just know how to take objectives

replies.body:
_le checks op.gg_

16 win 4 loss per last 20 games.... whats the problem here?
most of the deaths are from teamfight because i always engage and soak up all the enemy teams CD's, then my team just destroys them

As was already said, less deathes would be a plus, however that said, your probably being smart about your deaths looking at your stats.

Don't be worried about climbing, because if your winning and climbing then your doing good.

You're playing Swain, who is regarded as OP and being banned at the moment :D. Nah, but besides that, you probably know how to take objectives and are in a good mindset for ranked.

You could do with less deaths though.
